5. What is your favorite concept in preprocessing? What is the concept that gives you the most trouble?

My favorite concept by far is the ability to nest. It saves alot of time from typing alot of redundant code over and over. The concept that gives me the most troulbe would be mixins. Understanding mixins is not difficult, but knowing how to utilize them efficiently is what I find very difficult to do. 